	serial "SLUS-20346"
	description "AirForce Delta Strike continues the AirForce Delta series with over 60 missions and more than 130 planes, including historical WWII planes, Konami arcade classics -- Vic Viper, from Gradius -- and modern hybrid fighter-bombers. Players must choose from over 20 pilots, each with distinct strengths and weaknesses. Gameplay takes users through an open ended plot with interplanetary missions, villains, and plenty of squad-based aerial combat."
