game (
	name "Ape Escape 3 (USA)"
	serial "SCUS-97501"
	description "The apes escape on North American PS2s for a third time, and it will take more than a heroic kid with a simple net to trap them all before their mischief infects the minds of innocent folks around the world. Once again under the influence of the villainous Specter, siren-helmeted simians have invaded the local television station and begun to broadcast a signal designed to cloud the minds of viewers. Young Yumi and Kei must explore the station and round up all the rogue primates, before the damage is done. In addition to the regular compliment of ape-nabbing gadgets, the heroes can morph into special forms -- such as a ninja, a cowboy, or a chivalrous knight -- in order to take on whatever challenges those malicious monkeys throw at them this time around."
	developer "Sony"
	publisher "Sony"
