	serial "SLPM-62411"
	description "Smash Cars gives players control of 13 RC cars -- such as Road Rage, Warhammer, Tornado Buggy, Stormbringer, and a custom-created CCCP -- and offers 13 racing worlds, including Mexico, Russia, the Caribbean, Arizona, and Hawaii. Gameplay includes racing, winning upgrades and promotions, finding hidden secrets, shortcuts, crocodiles, and punks. Enormous jumps give users a chance to perform high-flying tricks, and the steering allows spins, fish-tails, wheelies, and hydroplaning."
