	serial "SLPS-25374"
	description "Based on the 1963 movie starring Steve McQueen, Richard Attenborough, and James Garner, The Great Escape has PlayStation 2 owners leading a squad of prisoners in their bid to free themselves from the German prisoner-of-war camp known as Stalag Luft III. The action takes place from a third-person perspective as players look to complete each of the game's three distinct phases. The first part involves acquiring the right equipment to ensure success, including digging tools, wire cutters, disguises, identity cards, and so forth. Stealth is an important element during this initial phase, as players must sneak around heavily guarded areas to obtain the tools needed for their survival."
