game (
	name "Naruto - Narutimate Hero 2 (Japan)"
	serial "SLPS-25398"
	description "Naruto: Ultimate Ninja 2 invites gamers back into the brawl as they work their way through three modes of play alone or with friends. Following the single-player storyline, gamers lead Naruto through 16 stages of combat located in the woods, on the water, among temple ruins, and on the streets of an Asian city. In each battle players earn cash and experience points. While gamers may spend experience to increase speed, agility, or defense, the cash is spent on voice samples, character models, video clips. Players may also perfect their moves in the 'Practice' zone before fighting friends in 'Vs.' mode with characters including Gara, Kiba, Rock Lee, and Sasake."
