	description "The sequel to the shmup Philosoma happens to be, of all things, a horror game. After the destruction of Planet 220, the ship Gallant is damaged and much of the crew turned into zombies by an unknown alien lifeform. To find out what’s going on and escape the disaster, the player must switch between three characters (Jude Sutcliffe, Renee Hearn & Alia Hoebraten) in different sections of the ship to solve the mystery. Despite being a Japan-only game, all the voice acting is in English, so importers unable to read Japanese will at least have some understanding of the plot."
