game (
	name "Pop 'n Taisen Puzzle Dama Online (Japan)"
	serial "SLPM-62464"
	description "Pop'n Taisen: Puzzle Dama Online is a puzzle game from Konami, featuring characters from the company's long-running Pop 'N Music series. The objective is to group three balls of matching colors in a Tetris-like environment. You need to rely on quick reflexes and your ability to plan large combos -- especially when playing in the two-player 'taisen' mode. The more balls you remove at the same time, the more problems you cause on your adversary's side. The game features plenty of funny animations from the 'Pop'n' cast as well as a range of hidden characters, some of which are completely new. As the name suggests, Pop'n Taisen: Puzzle Dama Online also features online play that lets two players go up against each other in head-to-head puzzle battles."
	developer "Konami"
	publisher "Konami"
	releaseyear "2004"
	releasemonth "3"
	releaseday "30"
	users "2"
	genre "Puzzle"
	rom (
