	serial "SLPM-62044"
	description "The game series that began as Re-Volt has come to the Playstation 2, bringing remote-controlled action and mayhem to the next-generation system. While most racing games seek to bring the realistic feel of driving an actual car into the virtual world, RC Revenge Pro tries to capture the whimsy of RC racing. RC Revenge Pro has decidedly kart-style overtones and will take you through tracks that could only exist in the imagination of those who designed them."
