game (
	name "Rumble Roses (Japan)"
	serial "SLKA-25234"
	description "Konami rolls out a wrestling game for the PS2 where players control an all-vixen cast looking to suplex, dropkick, and fling mud in the faces of their opponents. Rumble Roses features 11 scantly clad, and at times very dirty, female characters. In Mud Mode, players will take on their opponents in a mud wrestling match designed to reveal more than just wrestling expertise. Classic wrestling moves are available, such as suplexes, kicks, and flying elbows, as well as the ability for players to taunt and insult their opponents, which can provide advantages in the ring."
