game (
	name "Scared Rider Xechs (Japan)"
	serial "SLPM-55266"
	description "When an alien invasion gets into gear, six boys are recruited to combat the nefarious threat from outer space. Troops of otherworldly aliens are invading earth. To protect the planet and humanity, six chosen youths are recruited into the Scared Rider team under you, their commander. In any other genre of game, there'd be a cast of trigger-happy grunts who blast away in blazing action sequences. However, Scared Rider Xechsisn't a shooter nor is it a tactical simulation. SRX is an otome game or a boy's love adventure where the protagonist is girl named Akira Asagi and she's surrounded by six hunky guys whom she directs against the aliens."
