	name "Silent Scope 2 - Innocent Sweeper (Japan)"
	serial "SLPM-62085"
	description "A radical terrorist organization has obtained a tremendous payload of dangerous chemical weapons and is currently unleashing a master plan to spread them across the free world. A full-scale attack against these terrorist won't work because it will simply result in an immediate bio-weapon counter strike. Secrecy and stealth is needed, and the famous sniper Agent Falcon seems to be the best man for the job. But this time, he won't go it alone, as the mysterious rogue mercenary Jackal, long a rival of Falcon, has made it clear he's going on this mission, as well."
