	serial "SLPM-65449"
	description "Players can once again shake what their momma gave them with the release of SSX 3, the high-flying snowboarding game that emphasizes speed and aerial stunts above all else. This installment does away with the separate courses found in the first two games and instead features one giant interconnected world filled with different competitions, hidden collectibles, and new elements called Big Challenges. In addition to new courses, characters, and tricks, SSX 3 offers such visual enhancements as character shadows as well as snow that sparkles in the sun and drifts in the wind."
