game (
	name "Summon Night 3 (Japan)"
	serial "SCAJ-20034"
	description "The third installment in the Summon Night series (Summon Night and Summon Night 2 appeared on PlayStation), the game casts players in the role of boy or a girl (Rexx or Aty) who is mentored by a military hero, hones his/her skill with the blade, and sets out on a big adventure. The game's quest is driven forward by anime-style (mostly still) cutscenes with full voice-over narration, while battles use the Quest/Square-style isometric strategy map setup. The PlayStation 2 release improves over its predecessor with more elaborate magic animations, voice content and an overall better looking graphic presentation."
