game (
	name "Tenshou Gakuen Gekkouroku (Japan)"
	serial "SLPM-66566"
	description "Surrounded by a beautiful valley, Mount Fuji is not only the most famous mountain of Japan, but also - according to old legends - the home of gods. It is said that once the country plunges into the age of disasters, the soul of the saviour will be reincarnated in one of the people living near the mountain. Presently, a devastating, menacing power appears on the horizon - the heavenly demons, the Tenma. You control Asuka Inami, a student at the Tenshou Highschool, which is situated in the valley near Mount Fuji. With the help of your fellow students - including those of the rival military academy Tsukuyomu, composed of members of anti-Tenma brigade - you'll have to discover your true destination and to save your land."
