	serial "SCPS-15035"
	description "The Keihin Kyuukou - Train Simulator Real: With Japanese citizens marching to the beat of a frenetic drum, time is of the essence when you're the man who takes salarymen, students and secretaries to their jobs and rounds every morning. Accelerate, decelerate and toot your horn whilst passing intersections to ward off potential passers. A follow up to The Yamate Line from earlier this year, Sony trains it's development skills on the competing Keihin bullet line in Japan. Big iron buffs may thrill to the use of live video footage in this game where complete routes have been transposed from video to PS2."
