	name "Trouble Fortune Company - Happy Cure (Japan)"
	serial "SLPM-66626"
	description "Trouble Fortune Company Happy Cure: Trouble Fortune takes place in a high school, where you assume the role of a female student named Tsuzuri Kunisaki. The story is about our heroine Tsuzuri whose mother is a fortune teller. One day her mom Sakura goes missing in action, leaving Tsuzuri and her brother Amane, saying she’s gone to look for their father. She leaves without saying where she’s going and how long she’ll be gone and now all of her fortune telling customers demand to see her. It’s up to Tsuzuri to train (aka for you to raise stats) so that she can become a super fortune teller and snag that man."
