game (
	name "True Fortune (Japan)"
	serial "SLPS-25880"
	description "True Fortune: I had a dream. The dream I had many times before. A sad parting dream.... 'I'll give you these cards.' 'Oh, beautiful cards. Thank you.' She was my best friend.... I was very sad..., but I still remember her last word. 'Well, when you get older, these cards will be useful. Don't lose them!' 'Ok, I'll surely keep them!' An alarm clock rings and I wake up. 'Oh, where did I put those cards? Well, maybe here....' They are called the True Fortune Cards and each card has a face of a boy. He still doesn't know that the boys he will meet in the near future have the same faces written on the cards...."
	developer "Enterbrain / TwoFive"
	publisher "Enterbrain"
	releaseyear "2008"
	releasemonth "9"
	releaseday "25"
	users "1"
	genre "Adventure"
	rom (
