game (
	name "Urban Reign (Japan)"
	serial "SCAJ-20152"
	description "Players take the role of a mercenary thug, hired to serve as bodyguard to a prominent street gang leader, in this beat-'em-up adventure by Namco. Throughout Urban Reign's approximately 100 short missions, the player's character will make new friends and battle many, many foes, using both bare knuckles and improvised weaponry. The game's fighting engine is inspired by the solid mechanics of Tekken and Soul Calbur, and selected characters from those popular Namco fighting game series play cameo roles in Urban Reign."
