game (
	name "Donkey Xote (Europe)"
	serial "SLES-54838"
	description "We all know Don Quixote's version of the story, and now for the first time, we will get to know the REAL truth, what Don Quixote's deliriums and hallucinations impeded him from telling the whole story, which is where Rucio, Sancho's donkey steps in. Rucio in his high esteem towards the wishful Knight, also dreams of being a worthy knights steed, a brave and noble horse in fact. Rucio shares the adventures of Don Quixote, his horse Rocinante, his master Sancho Panza and himself throughout Castilla la Mancha in Spain."
