		name "Dragon Ball Z - Budokai (Europe).cue"
	)
)

game (
	name "Dragon Ball Z - Budokai 2 (Europe)"
	serial "SLES-51839"
	description "One of the most popular anime franchises in the United States returns to the PlayStation 2 console for another round of super-powered fighting. While revisiting the colorful presentation and basic 3D fighting gameplay style of 2002's original Dragon Ball Z: Budokai, the battles of this sequel are bolstered by additional options, more powerful 'Ki' energy moves, and new combo attacks. Graphics have a more cel-shaded look, with cartoon-like outlines around characters and objects."
	developer "Dimps Corporation"
	publisher "Atari"
	releaseyear "2003"
	releasemonth "11"
