		name "Donkey Xote (Europe).cue"
	)
)

game (
	name "Headhunter - Redemption (Europe)"
	serial "SLES-52511"
	description "As bounty hunters in a disturbing future, players must sneak by, strong-arm, and shoot down those who would flee from justice. This action-adventure is built upon the story and gameplay of the original Headhunter (also developed by Amuze), released in 2001 for European Dreamcasts and ported to North American PS2s the following year. Unlike the original, however, Headhunter: Redemption offers two main characters and two different, urban game worlds for them to patrol and protect."
