game (
	name "Scarface - The world is yours (Europe)"
	serial "SLES-54182"
	description "It's time to 'make way for the bad guy' in this adaptation of Brian De Palma's 1983 film starring Al Pacino as Cuban drug dealer Tony Montana. The game picks up where the movie left off, albeit with the stunning revelation that Montana isn't dead. Montana survives the assassination attempt and vows revenge on the kingpin who nearly put him out of commission: Alejandro Sosa. Players assume the role of power-hungry Montana in his bid to reclaim his cocaine empire and extravagant lifestyle. This, of course, means resorting to graphic violence and colorful profanity as a means of 'persuasion.'"
	developer "Radical Entertainment"
	publisher "Vivendi Universal Games"
	releaseyear "2006"
	releasemonth "10"
	releaseday "13"
	users "1"
	genre "Action"
	rom (
