game (
	name "Scooby Doo & The Spooky Swamp (Europe)"
	serial "SLES-55609"
	description "Scooby-Doo! and the Spooky Swamp is an open-world action-adventure game for fans of the long-running franchise, starring the whole Mystery Inc. gang. 'Those meddling kids' will need to work together to make it through the game's most difficult challenges. Gamers can play as Scooby, Shaggy, Velma, Daphne, or Fred, swapping on-the-fly to make use of each character's special abilities when they're most needed, and a second player can join the action at almost any time, to help overcome obstacles through teamwork."
