	serial "SLES-51841"
	description "SpyHunter returns for more racing combat action in this multi-platform sequel, which introduces several new features to the core gameplay of its 2001 predecessor. While players still drive the G-8155 Interceptor from a third-person perspective in an attempt to complete mission objectives, the vehicle now transforms into an off-road transport, motorcycle, and a snow ski. The terrorist organization known as Nostra is once again behind a diabolical plot to control the world. Master spy Alec Sects must eliminate as many enemy vehicles as possible while neutralizing key installations and areas under hostile control."
