		name "Star Wars - Racer Revenge (Europe).cue"
	)
)

game (
	name "Star Wars - Super Bombad Racing (Europe)"
	serial "SLES-50204"
	description "Star Wars: Super Bombad Racing is Lucas Learning's contribution to the kart-racing genre, which has played host to several well-known licenses and mascots since the 1992 debut of Super Mario Kart. Featuring super-deformed (small bodies with large heads) characters from the Star Wars universe, Super Bombad Racing is a no-holds barred, mad dash across nine courses, each of which is set on a recognizable world from the film series."
	developer "Lucas Learning"
	publisher "Lucasarts"
	releaseyear "2001"
