	serial "SLES-50033"
	description "Swing Away Golf, a less-than-serious take on the game, may remind many of Hot Shots Golf, and that's not surprising since it was developed by many of the same designers. Seven different golfers are available initially, but success in the tournament mode will unlock three more, as well as additional courses, golf clubs and gameplay modes. It's also possible to design your own dream course or have one randomly generated. And although it's not a strict simulation, the subtleties of real golf have been included for demanding players."
