game (
	name "The Mummy Returns (Europe)"
	serial "SLES-50510"
	description "Following the premise first introduced in the movie of the same name, The Mummy Returns casts players in the role of the evil mummy Imhotep or valiant adventurer Rick 'O Connell. Viewed from a third-person perspective, players must guide the character of their choosing through 12 stages, spanning familiar locales from the movie such as London, Cairo, and the ruins of Hamunaptara. All while fighting off enemies, traversing treacherous jumps and collecting items that will help them on their journey. Though their quests are similar, each character possesses different abilities and weapons. Rick 'O Connell has access to a variety of weapons, including pistols, shotguns, and swords, but must pick up health items to stay alive. Imhotep, however, wields magic and can absorb the souls of his enemies to replenish his health."
