game (
	name "Wallace & Gromit in Project Zoo (Europe)"
	serial "SLES-51372"
	description "The Claymation exploits of Wallace and Gromit move from Academy Award-winning short films to PlayStation 2 in a title that has players guiding Gromit (with his loyal owner Wallace tagging along) in a quest to free imprisoned baby animals. It seems the conniving penguin Feathers McGraw has enslaved the zoo's critters in order to unearth valuable gems to fuel his beloved Diamond-O-Matic. The result is an adventure spanning five main levels of exploration, puzzle solving, and the trademark humor for which the series is known."
