	serial "SLES-51958"
	description "Whiplash is a platformer video game for the PlayStation 2 and Xbox where a long-tailed weasel chained to a rabbit must work together to escape from a product testing corporation known as Genron and putting the fat boss out of commission . The game is a basic platformer, with Spanx (the weasel) as the main character, and Redmond (the rabbit) as more of a tool."
